data.eml:eml: Archaeocercus gen. nov. (Hymenoptera, Chalcidoidea, Encyrtidae) from Late Eocene Rovno Amber

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Simutnik, S. A., Perkovsky, E. E. (2018): Archaeocercus gen. nov. (Hymenoptera, Chalcidoidea, Encyrtidae) from Late Eocene Rovno Amber. Zootaxa 4441 (3): 543-548, DOI: https://doi.org/10.11646/zootaxa.4441.3.8
